"We also check whether the player is moving so we can call ``play()`` or "
"``stop()`` on the AnimatedSprite2D."
msgstr ""
"Také ověříme zda se hráč pohybuje, takže na můžeme volat metody ``play ()`` "
"nebo ``stop ()`` uzlu AnimatedSprite."

